---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout seoPage="home" activeNav="home">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="section" id="hero" style="display:flex;align-items:center;min-height:100dvh;padding-top:100px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:52%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:none;" aria-hidden="true">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 30%;opacity:0.35;">
            <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--bg) 30%,transparent 60%),linear-gradient(180deg,var(--bg) 0%,transparent 25%,transparent 75%,var(--bg) 100%);"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),transparent);opacity:0.3;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
            <div style="max-width:820px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up">
                    <span class="accent-line"></span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--fg-2);letter-spacing:0.05em;">Kita bikin website, bukan jual jasa koding <span style="font-size:1rem;">🤙</span></span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="t-display reveal reveal-up d-1" style="margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:24px;">
                    website <span style="color:var(--accent);">webkalcer</span>,<br>
                    bikin bisnis kamu<br>
                    <span class="punch">naik kelas</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-subtitle reveal reveal-up d-2" style="max-width:540px;">
                    <span class="brand">web</span><span class="brand-a">kalcer</span> bikin website profesional tanpa ribet. Dari desain sampe launching, kami urus semua.
                </p>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-3" style="display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:40px;">
                    <a href="#kontak" class="btn btn-solid">Mulai Konsultasi</a>
                    <a href="#layanan" class="btn btn-ghost">Lihat Layanan</a>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-4" style="display:flex;gap:40px;margin-top:64px;">
                    <div>
                        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg);">50+</div>
                        <div class="t-small">Proyek selesai</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg);">98%</div>
                        <div class="t-small">Klien puas</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg);">3+</div>
                        <div class="t-small">Tahun pengalaman</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LAYANAN -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="layanan" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:start;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up">
                    <span class="accent-line"></span>
                    <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:16px;">Layanan yang<br>tepat sasaran.</h2>
                    <p class="t-subtitle">Bukan template. Setiap website kami rancang dari nol sesuai kebutuhan bisnis dan karakter brand kamu. Pilih layanan yang paling cocok, atau diskusi dulu - kami bantu tentuin.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;">
                        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 3l14 9-14 9V3z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex:1;">
                            <h3 class="t-h3">Landing Page</h3>
                            <p class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Halaman satu halaman yang fokus banget ke konversi — cocok buat campaign, produk baru, atau personal branding. Desainnya clean, loadingnya cepet, dan bikin pengunjung langsung action.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-up d-1" style="padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;">
                        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex:1;">
                            <h3 class="t-h3">Company Profile</h3>
                            <p class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Website multi-halaman yang narikin cerita brand kamu secara profesional — dari visi misi, portfolio, sampai tim. Biar calon klien percaya dan yakin pilih kamu.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-up d-2" style="padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;">
                        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/><circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/><path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 002 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 002-1.61L23 6H6"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex:1;">
                            <h3 class="t-h3">Toko Online</h3>
                            <p class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">E-commerce siap pakai dengan payment gateway, manajemen stok, dan dashboard admin. Pelanggan bisa belanja langsung, kamu tinggal terima order — urusan teknis biar kami yang urus.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-up d-3" style="padding:24px 0;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;">
                        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex:1;">
                            <h3 class="t-h3">UI/UX Design</h3>
                            <p class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Desain antarmuka yang intuitif dan engaging — mulai dari wireframe, prototipe, sampai visual final. Cocok buat kamu yang butuh fondasi desain yang mateng sebelum di-develop.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROSES -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="proses" style="background:var(--bg-2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 80px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;">
                    <span class="accent-line"></span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="t-h1 reveal reveal-up d-1">Cara kami bekerja.</h2>
                <p class="t-subtitle reveal reveal-up d-2" style="margin-top:12px;">Transparan dari awal sampai akhir. Kamu lihat progress setiap tahap, tanpa drama, tanpa kejutan.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="padding:36px 28px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);position:relative;">
                    <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);opacity:0.15;position:absolute;top:20px;right:24px;line-height:1;">01</div>
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v10z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Konsultasi & Riset</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Kami dengar dulu kebutuhan kamu, analisis kompetitor, dan kasih rekomendasi yang tepat. Gratis, tanpa tekanan.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-1" style="padding:36px 28px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);position:relative;">
                    <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);opacity:0.15;position:absolute;top:20px;right:24px;line-height:1;">02</div>
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Desain & Bangun</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Tim kami buat desain dan develop websitenya. Kamu bisa lihat progress real-time dan kasih feedback langsung.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-2" style="padding:36px 28px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);position:relative;">
                    <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);opacity:0.15;position:absolute;top:20px;right:24px;line-height:1;">03</div>
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Launch & Tumbuh</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Website live. Kami bantu optimasi dan maintenance. Fokus kamu tinggal jalanin bisnis, urusan teknis biar kami yang urus.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TECH STACK -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="stack" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 60px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;">
                    <span class="accent-line"></span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="t-h1 reveal reveal-up d-1">Teknologi yang kami pakai.</h2>
                <p class="t-subtitle reveal reveal-up d-2" style="margin-top:12px;">Dari frontend sampai hosting, kami pake teknologi teruji biar hasilnya maksimal dan tahan lama.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-wrapper">
            <div class="stack-track">
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M7 19V5h4l6 12V5h4v14h-4l-6-12v12z"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">Next.js</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">React framework</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.5"/><ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="4.5" transform="rotate(60 12 12)"/><ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="4.5" transform="rotate(-60 12 12)"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">React</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">UI library</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2L2 21h20z"/><path d="M12 8l4 10H8z"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">Vue.js</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Frontend framework</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 3L3 21h18z"/><circle cx="12" cy="14" r="3" fill="var(--bg)"/><path d="M12 7l-2 5h4z"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">Astro</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Static site builder</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 20L12 4l8 16z"/><path d="M8 16h8"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">Supabase</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Backend &amp; database</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 20V4h16v4H8v2h12v4H8v2h12v4z"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">Laravel</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">PHP framework</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 6L4 12l6 6"/><path d="M14 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">PHP</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Server language</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="7" ry="3"/><path d="M5 5v11c0 2 3 3.5 7 3.5s7-1.5 7-3.5V5"/><path d="M5 10.5c0 2 3 3.5 7 3.5s7-1.5 7-3.5"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">MySQL</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Relational database</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-item">
                    <div class="stack-item-icon" style="color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-dim);"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M17 8c0-2.5-2-4-5-4S7 5.5 7 8c0 2.5 2 3.5 5 4s5 1.5 5 4-2 4-5 4-5-1.5-5-4"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="stack-item-name">SQLite</div>
                    <div class="stack-item-desc">Embedded database</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ANGKA -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="angka" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="stats-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:32px;text-align:center;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up">
                    <div class="counter" data-target="50" data-suffix="+" style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-0.03em;">50+</div>
                    <div class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Proyek selesai</div>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-1">
                    <div class="counter" data-target="98" data-suffix="%" style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-0.03em;">98%</div>
                    <div class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Klien puas</div>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-2">
                    <div class="counter" data-target="3" data-suffix="+" style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-0.03em;">3+</div>
                    <div class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Tahun aktif</div>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-3">
                    <div class="counter" data-target="100" data-suffix="%" style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-0.03em;">100%</div>
                    <div class="t-small" style="margin-top:4px;">Custom dari nol</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- KEUNGGULAN -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="keunggulan" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 80px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;">
                    <span class="accent-line"></span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="t-h1 reveal reveal-up d-1">Kenapa pilih <span class="brand">web</span><span class="brand-a">kalcer</span>?</h2>
                <p class="t-subtitle reveal reveal-up d-2" style="margin-top:12px;">Bukan cuma bikin website. Kami pastiin setiap detail berfungsi dan berdampak buat bisnis kamu.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="keunggulan-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--bg);">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">100% Custom Code</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Tidak ada template atau page builder. Setiap baris kode ditulis manual dari nol. Hasilnya ringan, cepat, dan bebas bloat.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-1" style="padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--bg);">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Transparan Sepenuhnya</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Kamu bisa lihat progress real-time, akses langsung ke project, dan tau persis apa yang dikerjakan. No black box, no drama.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-2" style="padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--bg);">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Cepat & Ringan</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Optimasi performa dari awal: gambar di-compress, kode minimalis, hosting cepet. Target loading di bawah 3 detik.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal reveal-up d-3" style="padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--bg);">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Support 24/7</h3>
                    <p class="t-small">Kalo ada masalah atau bingung tinggal chat via WhatsApp. Respon cepat, nggak pake sistem tiket yang lama.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONI -->
    <section class="section-sm" id="testimoni" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="margin-bottom:60px;">
                <span class="accent-line"></span>
                <h2 class="t-h1">Dengar dari klien kami.</h2>
                <p class="t-body reveal reveal-up d-1" style="margin-top:8px;">Mereka udah rasain langsung. Sekarang giliran kamu.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="display:flex;gap:28px;overflow-x:auto;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;padding-bottom:20px;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;scrollbar-width:thin;transition-delay:0.4s;">
                <div class="reveal reveal-up" style="flex:0 0 400px;scroll-snap-align:start;padding:36px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.2" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.5-.5-2-2-2H4c-1.5 0-2 .5-2 2v7c0 1.5.5 2 2 2c0 3.5 1 5 3 6v-2zm14 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.5-.5-2-2-2h-4c-1.5 0-2 .5-2 2v7c0 1.5.5 2 2 2c0 3.5 1 5 3 6v-2z"/></svg>
                    <p style="font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.7;color:var(--fg-2);margin-bottom:24px;">"Pelayanannya cepat dan desainnya sesuai banget sama brand kami. Responnya juga selalu cepat setiap kali ada request revisi."</p>
